{"id":201014,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/译者-《商业内幕》：图说中国改天换地的108个巨型/","date":"2011-12-09T12:31:28Z","modified":"2011-12-09T12:31:28Z","title":"译者 | 《商业内幕》：图说中国改天换地的108个巨型基建项目","content":"<p><b><span>核心提示：</span><span>一份包括108个项目的中国巨型基建项目名单在网上流传，</span><span>本文选择其中最炫的45个出来。</span><span>中国的项目建设速度是不是超过了市场的承受能力呢？</span></b></p>\n<p>原文：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/108-giant-chinese-infrastructure-projects-that-are-reshaping-the-world-2011-12?op=1\">108 Giant Chinese Infrastructure Projects That Are Reshaping The World</a><br />作者：Vivian Giang，Robert Johnson <br />发表：2011年12月5日<br />本文由译者志愿者“MyPicture”翻译，译者志愿者校对。</p>\n<div><img src=\"http://static8.businessinsider.com/image/4edd0a976bb3f74e33000016/china.jpg\" alt=\"China\" border=\"0\" /></div>\n<p>【原文配图】Image: wikipedia commons</p>\n<p>中国有句古话：“要想富，先修路。”</p>\n<p>确实，他们已经修了不少的路：在过去的一年中，我们已经看到了世界上最长的跨海大桥，最长的输气管道，以及超越其他所有人的高速公路。</p>\n<p>基础建设的动力是不可思议的。一个108个巨型工程的列表在中国留言版上广为流传，我们挑选了其中最炫的45个展示出来。</p>\n<p>从遍布大陆的高速公路，到最大的风力发电基地，到连接欧洲和印度的现代丝绸之路，到沙漠中的新城，中国正在展示什么才叫“集中力量办大事”。</p>\n<p>1亿零200万美元：平塘望远镜，世界上最大的射电望远镜将于2016年建成。   <br /><img title=\"102-million-the-pingtang-telescope-will-be-the-worlds-largest-radio-telescope-when-completed-in-2016.jpg\" alt=\"102-million-the-pingtang-telescope-will-be-the-worlds-largest-radio-telescope-when-completed-in-2016.jpg\" src=\"http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/4ddacd16cadcbba62b050000-590/102-million-the-pingtang-telescope-will-be-the-worlds-largest-radio-telescope-when-completed-in-2016.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>1亿7600万美元：上海同步辐射实验室承担中国最重要的科研项目，是中国最昂贵的实验设施。<br /><img title=\"176-million-shanghai-synchrotron-radiation-laboratory-conducts-chinas-major-scientific-projects-and-is-the-countrys-most-expensive-research-facility.jpg\" alt=\"176-million-shanghai-synchrotron-radiation-laboratory-conducts-chinas-major-scientific-projects-and-is-the-countrys-most-expensive-research-facility.jpg\" src=\"http://static8.businessinsider.com/image/4ddac35b4bd7c84238000000-590/176-million-shanghai-synchrotron-radiation-laboratory-conducts-chinas-major-scientific-projects-and-is-the-countrys-most-expensive-research-facility.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>2亿美元：广州歌剧院是中国最大的三个剧院之一，由建筑师扎哈•哈迪德设计。<br /><img title=\"200-million-the-guangzhou-opera-house-is-one-of-the-three-biggest-theaters-in-china-designed-by-architect-zaha-hadid.jpg\" alt=\"200-million-the-guangzhou-opera-house-is-one-of-the-three-biggest-theaters-in-china-designed-by-architect-zaha-hadid.jpg\" src=\"http://static8.businessinsider.com/image/4ddab7b54bd7c83321210000-590/200-million-the-guangzhou-opera-house-is-one-of-the-three-biggest-theaters-in-china-designed-by-architect-zaha-hadid.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>3亿6800万美元：海南电网项目是中国的第一个水下跨海电网，将连接海南岛与中国大陆。<br /><img title=\"368-million-the-hainan-power-grid-project-is-chinas-first-underwater-cross-sea-power-grid-and-will-link-the-southern-island-of-hainan-to-mainland-china.jpg\" alt=\"368-million-the-hainan-power-grid-project-is-chinas-first-underwater-cross-sea-power-grid-and-will-link-the-southern-island-of-hainan-to-mainland-china.jpg\" src=\"http://static6.businessinsider.com/image/4ddbc343cadcbbb747580000-590/368-million-the-hainan-power-grid-project-is-chinas-first-underwater-cross-sea-power-grid-and-will-link-the-southern-island-of-hainan-to-mainland-china.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<p>4亿7300万美元：秦岭隧道是中国最长的公路隧道。<br /><img title=\"473-million-the-qinling-tunnel-is-the-longest-highway-tunnel-in-china.jpg\" alt=\"473-million-the-qinling-tunnel-is-the-longest-highway-tunnel-in-china.jpg\" src=\"http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/4ddab958ccd1d5f412250000-590/473-million-the-qinling-tunnel-is-the-longest-highway-tunnel-in-china.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>7亿1700万美元：喀什—和田铁路连接了塔里木盆地西南部的所有城市。<br /><img title=\"717-million-the-kashgar-hotan-railway-connects-all-the-cities-and-towns-of-the-southwestern-tarim-basin.jpg\" alt=\"717-million-the-kashgar-hotan-railway-connects-all-the-cities-and-towns-of-the-southwestern-tarim-basin.jpg\" src=\"http://static6.businessinsider.com/image/4ddac1f8cadcbb69160b0000-590/717-million-the-kashgar-hotan-railway-connects-all-the-cities-and-towns-of-the-southwestern-tarim-basin.jpg\" /> </p>\n<p>7亿6000万美元：中国中央电视台总部由6个水平和垂直部分环绕组成，环绕周长达1,551,837英尺。<br /><img title=\"760-million-china-central-tv-headquarters-is-a-loop-of-six-horizontal-and-vertical-sections-covering-1551837-ft.jpg\" alt=\"760-million-china-central-tv-headquarters-is-a-loop-of-six-horizontal-and-vertical-sections-covering-1551837-ft.jpg\" src=\"http://static6.businessinsider.com/image/4ddaa68ccadcbbb6680c0000-590/760-million-china-central-tv-headquarters-is-a-loop-of-six-horizontal-and-vertical-sections-covering-1551837-ft.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>9亿美元：天荒坪蓄能水电站是亚洲最大的水电工程，对于中国东部的电力供应有着举足轻重的作用。<br /><img title=\"900-million-the-tianhuangping-hydroelectric-project-is-the-biggest-in-asia-and-plays-a-vital-role-in-providing-power-supply-in-eastern-china.jpg\" alt=\"900-million-the-tianhuangping-hydroelectric-project-is-the-biggest-in-asia-and-plays-a-vital-role-in-providing-power-supply-in-eastern-china.jpg\" src=\"http://static8.businessinsider.com/image/4ddbe29649e2ae145d230000-590/900-million-the-tianhuangping-hydroelectric-project-is-the-biggest-in-asia-and-plays-a-vital-role-in-providing-power-supply-in-eastern-china.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>11亿美元：上海柏悦酒店是世界上第二高的酒店，位于上海环球金融中心79层。<br /><img title=\"11-billion-the-shanghai-world-financial-center-project-is-home-to-the-second-highest-hotel-in-the-world-the-park-hyatt-shanghai-is-on-the-79th-floor.jpg\" alt=\"11-billion-the-shanghai-world-financial-center-project-is-home-to-the-second-highest-hotel-in-the-world-the-park-hyatt-shanghai-is-on-the-79th-floor.jpg\" src=\"http://static6.businessinsider.com/image/4ddaace249e2ae942f0a0000-590/11-billion-the-shanghai-world-financial-center-project-is-home-to-the-second-highest-hotel-in-the-world-the-park-hyatt-shanghai-is-on-the-79th-floor.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>13亿美元：“波罗的海明珠”项目是中国最大的国外开发项目，位于俄罗斯圣彼得堡郊外，包括住宅和商业地产。<br /><img title=\"13-billion-the-baltic-pearl-project-is-chinas-largest-foreign-development-project-and-consists-of-residential-and-commercial-properties-outside-st-petersburg-russia.jpg\" alt=\"13-billion-the-baltic-pearl-project-is-chinas-largest-foreign-development-project-and-consists-of-residential-and-commercial-properties-outside-st-petersburg-russia.jpg\" src=\"http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/4def7ec149e2ae5950210000-590/13-billion-the-baltic-pearl-project-is-chinas-largest-foreign-development-project-and-consists-of-residential-and-commercial-properties-outside-st-petersburg-russia.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>17亿美元： 武汉天兴洲长江大桥位于武汉市，是一个横跨长江的铁路公路两用大桥。 <br /><img title=\"17-billion-the-wuhan-tianxingzhou-yangtze-river-bridge-is-a-combined-road-and-rail-bridge-across-the-yangtze-river-in-the-city-of-wuhan.jpg\" alt=\"17-billion-the-wuhan-tianxingzhou-yangtze-river-bridge-is-a-combined-road-and-rail-bridge-across-the-yangtze-river-in-the-city-of-wuhan.jpg\" src=\"http://static7.businessinsider.com/image/4dda9f0949e2aee50a140000-590/17-billion-the-wuhan-tianxingzhou-yangtze-river-bridge-is-a-combined-road-and-rail-bridge-across-the-yangtze-river-in-the-city-of-wuhan.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>17亿美元：2005年竣工的南京地铁每年有1亿8千万人次使用。<br /><img title=\"17-billion-the-nanjing-metro-line-was-completed-in-2005-and-is-used-by-almost-180-million-people-a-year.jpg\" alt=\"17-billion-the-nanjing-metro-line-was-completed-in-2005-and-is-used-by-almost-180-million-people-a-year.jpg\" src=\"http://static8.businessinsider.com/image/4ddaaaa8cadcbb61700e0000-590/17-billion-the-nanjing-metro-line-was-completed-in-2005-and-is-used-by-almost-180-million-people-a-year.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>18亿美元：上海长江隧道大桥是世界第五长的斜拉式大桥。<br /><img title=\"18-billion-the-shanghai-yangtze-river-tunnel-and-bridge-is-the-fifth-longest-cable-stayed-bridge-in-the-world.jpg\" alt=\"18-billion-the-shanghai-yangtze-river-tunnel-and-bridge-is-the-fifth-longest-cable-stayed-bridge-in-the-world.jpg\" src=\"http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/4ddac2394bd7c896322d0000-590/18-billion-the-shanghai-yangtze-river-tunnel-and-bridge-is-the-fifth-longest-cable-stayed-bridge-in-the-world.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>19亿美元：成都双流机场每年将运送3500万旅客。<br />.<img title=\"19-billion-the-chengdu-shuangliu-airport-will-handle-35-million-passengers-annually.jpg\" alt=\"19-billion-the-chengdu-shuangliu-airport-will-handle-35-million-passengers-annually.jpg\" src=\"http://static7.businessinsider.com/image/4ddac18749e2ae5260050000-590/19-billion-the-chengdu-shuangliu-airport-will-handle-35-million-passengers-annually.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>21.2亿美元：武汉火车站为世界上最快的火车提供服务，其时速达217英里（译注：约350公里）。<br /><img title=\"212-billion-the-wuhan-railway-station-serves-the-worlds-fastest-trains-at-217-mph.jpg\" alt=\"212-billion-the-wuhan-railway-station-serves-the-worlds-fastest-trains-at-217-mph.jpg\" src=\"http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/4def7bcf4bd7c8e05d0a0000-590/212-billion-the-wuhan-railway-station-serves-the-worlds-fastest-trains-at-217-mph.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>22亿美元： 128层的上海中心大厦将于2014年竣工，届时将成为中国最高、世界第二高的摩天大楼。<br /><img title=\"22-billion-at-128-stories-the-shanghai-tower-will-be-the-tallest-skyscraper-in-china-and-the-second-tallest-in-the-world-when-completed-in-2014.jpg\" alt=\"22-billion-at-128-stories-the-shanghai-tower-will-be-the-tallest-skyscraper-in-china-and-the-second-tallest-in-the-world-when-completed-in-2014.jpg\" src=\"http://static8.businessinsider.com/image/4def7c15ccd1d5d253150000-590/22-billion-at-128-stories-the-shanghai-tower-will-be-the-tallest-skyscraper-in-china-and-the-second-tallest-in-the-world-when-completed-in-2014.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>22亿美元：拥有世界最大规模核反应装置的秦山核电站二期将成为秦山电厂的一部分。<br /><img title=\"22-billion-the-qinshan-nuclear-power-phase-ii-will-add-to-the-qinshan-plant-and-have-the-most-nuclear-reactors-of-any-site-in-the-world.jpg\" alt=\"22-billion-the-qinshan-nuclear-power-phase-ii-will-add-to-the-qinshan-plant-and-have-the-most-nuclear-reactors-of-any-site-in-the-world.jpg\" src=\"http://static6.businessinsider.com/image/4ddaa8a2cadcbbb768120000-590/22-billion-the-qinshan-nuclear-power-phase-ii-will-add-to-the-qinshan-plant-and-have-the-most-nuclear-reactors-of-any-site-in-the-world.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>28.8亿美元：红沿河核电站将成为中国东北的第一个核电站，年发电量将达到4.5亿千瓦时。<br /><img title=\"288-billion-the-hongyanhe-nuclear-power-plant-is-the-first-nuclear-power-station-in-northeastern-china-and-will-reach-45-billion-kwh-annually.jpg\" alt=\"288-billion-the-hongyanhe-nuclear-power-plant-is-the-first-nuclear-power-station-in-northeastern-china-and-will-reach-45-billion-kwh-annually.jpg\" src=\"http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/4ddbbb67cadcbb1f3e110000-590/288-billion-the-hongyanhe-nuclear-power-plant-is-the-first-nuclear-power-station-in-northeastern-china-and-will-reach-45-billion-kwh-annually.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>30亿美元：加蓬贝林加铁矿是中国在非洲最大的开采项目。<br /><img title=\"3-billion-the-great-gabon-belinga-iron-ore-mine-is-chinas-largest-african-mining-operation.jpg\" alt=\"3-billion-the-great-gabon-belinga-iron-ore-mine-is-chinas-largest-african-mining-operation.jpg\" src=\"http://static7.businessinsider.com/image/4def8011cadcbb8550000000-590/3-billion-the-great-gabon-belinga-iron-ore-mine-is-chinas-largest-african-mining-operation.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>33亿美元：天津近海钻井平台是中国近海石油开发的国家级基地。 <br /><img title=\"33-billion-the-tianjin-offshore-drilling-rig-is-chinas-national-base-for-offshore-oil-development.jpg\" alt=\"33-billion-the-tianjin-offshore-drilling-rig-is-chinas-national-base-for-offshore-oil-development.jpg\" src=\"http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/4ddae60fcadcbb3b501a0000-590/33-billion-the-tianjin-offshore-drilling-rig-is-chinas-national-base-for-offshore-oil-development.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>35亿美元：北京首都国际机场航站楼是中国最大的单体建筑工程，世界上第三大建筑物。<br /><img title=\"35-billion-the-beijing-capital-international-airport-terminal-is-the-largest-single-construction-project-in-china-and-the-third-largest-building-in-the-world.jpg\" alt=\"35-billion-the-beijing-capital-international-airport-terminal-is-the-largest-single-construction-project-in-china-and-the-third-largest-building-in-the-world.jpg\" src=\"http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/4def813949e2aecc5b570000-590/35-billion-the-beijing-capital-international-airport-terminal-is-the-largest-single-construction-project-in-china-and-the-third-largest-building-in-the-world.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>45亿美元：临港新城，一个计划于2020年建成的城市，将为约100万人提供住房。<br /><img title=\"45-billion-lingang-new-city-a-planned-city-to-be-completed-in-2020-will-house-almost-1-million-people.jpg\" alt=\"45-billion-lingang-new-city-a-planned-city-to-be-completed-in-2020-will-house-almost-1-million-people.jpg\" src=\"http://static7.businessinsider.com/image/4bcf68267f8b9aea55860100-590/45-billion-lingang-new-city-a-planned-city-to-be-completed-in-2020-will-house-almost-1-million-people.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>63亿美元：向家坝水电站工程将会在2015年竣工，每年发电量为310亿千瓦时。<br /><img title=\"63-billion-the-xiangjiaba-hydro-power-project-is-expected-to-be-completed-by-2015-and-generate-31-billion-kwh-annually.jpg\" alt=\"63-billion-the-xiangjiaba-hydro-power-project-is-expected-to-be-completed-by-2015-and-generate-31-billion-kwh-annually.jpg\" src=\"http://static8.businessinsider.com/image/4dda947b49e2ae3470060000-590/63-billion-the-xiangjiaba-hydro-power-project-is-expected-to-be-completed-by-2015-and-generate-31-billion-kwh-annually.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>50亿美元：上海-杭州磁悬浮工程将会建造世界上最快的城市间列车，时速达到280英里每小时（每小时450公里）。<br /><img title=\"5-billionthe-shanghai-hangzhou-maglev-project-will-create-the-fastest-inter-city-train-in-the-world-at-280-mph.jpg\" alt=\"5-billionthe-shanghai-hangzhou-maglev-project-will-create-the-fastest-inter-city-train-in-the-world-at-280-mph.jpg\" src=\"http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/4ddab8ef4bd7c83921180000-590/5-billionthe-shanghai-hangzhou-maglev-project-will-create-the-fastest-inter-city-train-in-the-world-at-280-mph.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>63亿美元：北京南站，亚洲最大的火车站。<br /><img title=\"63-billion-the-beijing-south-railway-station-is-asias-largest-railway-station.jpg\" alt=\"63-billion-the-beijing-south-railway-station-is-asias-largest-railway-station.jpg\" src=\"http://static6.businessinsider.com/image/4dda9a2049e2aeca03000000-590/63-billion-the-beijing-south-railway-station-is-asias-largest-railway-station.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>65亿美元：中国与多个国家签署了协议，重建古代“丝绸之路”，连接中国、印度和欧洲。<br /><img title=\"65-billion-china-is-one-out-several-countries-that-signed-a-contract-to-re-construct-the-ancient-silk-road-linking-china-and-india-with-europe.jpg\" alt=\"65-billion-china-is-one-out-several-countries-that-signed-a-contract-to-re-construct-the-ancient-silk-road-linking-china-and-india-with-europe.jpg\" src=\"http://static8.businessinsider.com/image/4def8377ccd1d56c5f060000-590/65-billion-china-is-one-out-several-countries-that-signed-a-contract-to-re-construct-the-ancient-silk-road-linking-china-and-india-with-europe.jpg\" /><br /> <br />67.6亿美元：溪洛渡大坝将会是世界上第三高的大坝、中国第二大的水电站。<br /><img title=\"676-billion-xiluodu-dam-will-be-the-third-tallest-dam-in-the-world-and-second-largest-hydro-power-station-in-the-country.jpg\" alt=\"676-billion-xiluodu-dam-will-be-the-third-tallest-dam-in-the-world-and-second-largest-hydro-power-station-in-the-country.jpg\" src=\"http://static8.businessinsider.com/image/4dda9d3cccd1d55763290000-590/676-billion-xiluodu-dam-will-be-the-third-tallest-dam-in-the-world-and-second-largest-hydro-power-station-in-the-country.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>78.9亿美元：苏通大桥是世界上最长的斜拉索大桥。<br /><img title=\"789-billion-the-su-tong-yangtze-river-bridge-is-the-worlds-longest-cable-stayed-bridge.jpg\" alt=\"789-billion-the-su-tong-yangtze-river-bridge-is-the-worlds-longest-cable-stayed-bridge.jpg\" src=\"http://static8.businessinsider.com/image/4dda81c9ccd1d5ce302a0000-590/789-billion-the-su-tong-yangtze-river-bridge-is-the-worlds-longest-cable-stayed-bridge.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>80亿美元：上海洋山深水港将应对世界上最大的集装箱船舶。<br /><img title=\"8-billion-the-shanghai-yangshan-deep-water-port-project-will-handle-the-largest-container-ships-in-the-world.jpg\" alt=\"8-billion-the-shanghai-yangshan-deep-water-port-project-will-handle-the-la